content: I have loved both of these games so much! One really cool thing is, in hard core mode, the puzzles are different and more difficult than in casual mode. You can go back and forth between the two modes, too. Loved that! Worth every penny!
I enjoyed the first game so bought this one however I am unable to play it. I get through the opening story then it just stops running. Please fix this issue. Playing on a Samsung note3.
